---
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="bg-black min-h-[50vh] flex items-center">
  <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 py-16 w-full">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
        In-Person<br />PDR Training
      </h1>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gold my-4"></div>
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Hands-on training from industry-leading Master Technician Jim Mitchell. Learn real techniques on real vehicles in a real shop environment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Info -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-container mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
        Learn PDR In Person
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-body mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Real World PDR has offered hands-on, in-person training workshops in the past, and we're working on bringing them back. Our in-person sessions give you the opportunity to learn directly from Jim Mitchell in a real shop environment — no staged setups, no perfect conditions, just the real-world skills you need to succeed.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-body mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        In-person training covers everything from tool selection and proper lighting setup to advanced dent repair techniques. You'll get hands-on practice with real vehicles and personalized feedback to accelerate your learning.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-body mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        If you're interested in scheduling an in-person training session or want to be the first to know when our next workshop is available, reach out to us directly. We'd love to hear from you and help you take the next step in your PDR career.
      </p>

      <!-- Contact CTA -->
      <div class="bg-[#f9f9f9] rounded-lg p-8 md:p-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Get in Touch</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-body mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Contact us to learn about upcoming in-person training opportunities, schedule a session, or ask any questions about our hands-on workshops.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-6">
          <a
            href="mailto:Jim@jmdentrepair.com"
            class="bg-gold text-white font-semibold uppercase text-base px-8 py-3 rounded inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 tracking-wider hover:bg-[#f98608] transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z" />
            </svg>
            Email Us
          </a>
          <a
            href="/real-world-pdr-courses"
            class="border-2 border-gold text-black font-semibold uppercase text-base px-8 py-3 rounded inline-flex items-center justify-center tracking-wider hover:bg-gold hover:text-white transition-colors"
          >
            Browse Online Courses
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-body text-sm space-y-1">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-black">Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:Jim@jmdentrepair.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">Jim@jmdentrepair.com</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-black">Location:</strong> 423 Farabee Dr S, Lafayette, IN 47905
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- While You Wait -->
<section class="py-16 px-4 bg-black">
  <div class="max-w-container mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      Start Learning Today
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      While you wait for in-person training, our online courses let you start building PDR skills right away. From beginner fundamentals to advanced techniques — learn at your own pace.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="/pdr-101"
        class="bg-gold text-white font-semibold uppercase text-base px-8 py-3 rounded inline-block tracking-wider hover:bg-[#f98608] transition-colors"
      >
        PDR 101 — $55
      </a>
      <a
        href="/pdr-ultimate"
        class="border-2 border-gold text-white font-semibold uppercase text-base px-8 py-3 rounded inline-block tracking-wider hover:bg-gold transition-colors"
      >
        PDR Monthly
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
